// Man page for check
manCheck="CHECK(1)                         X Shell Manual                         CHECK(1)

<b>NAME</b>
    check - Verify user assignment
<b>SYNOPSIS</b>
    <b>check</b>
<b>DESCRIPTION</b>
    Verify the current user assignment when permissions are corrupted
    or you suspect X made an incorrect choice. If check finds a
    discrepancy, it will automatically reset the user.
<b>EXAMPLE:</b>
    <b>check</b>
    Verify and fix user assignment"